| id | c1_tint | c2_sint | c3_mint | c4_bint | c5_floa | c6_doub | c7_deci |
+----+---------+---------+---------+---------+---------+---------+---------+
|  1 |      11 |      12 |      13 |      14 |    15.1 |    16.5 |      17 |
|  2 |      21 |      22 |      23 |      24 |    25.1 |    26.5 |      27 |
|  3 |      31 |      32 |     400 |      34 |    35.1 |    36.5 |      37 |
|  5 |      41 |      52 |      53 |      54 |    55.1 |    56.5 |      57 |
+----+---------+---------+---------+---------+---------+---------+---------+
